file.name: Swagger.yml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: MLA Weights and Condition Scores Example
  version: 0.0.1
paths:
  /animal/{identifier}/scores:
    get:
      description: Returns the scores for the specified animal
      operationId: findScores
      parameters:
        - name: identifier
          in: path
          description: primary identifier for the animal
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: scores response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscScoreReference'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
    post:
      description: Uploads new scores for the animal
      operationId: addScores
      parameters:
        - name: identifier
          in: path
          description: primary identifier for the animal
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        description: new score events for the animal
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscScoreReference'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: animal response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscScoreReference'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
    put:
      description: Updates the score events for the specified animal
      operationId: updateScores
      parameters:
        - name: identifier
          in: path
          description: primary identifier for the animal
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        description: Updated score events for the animal
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscScoreReference'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: animal response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscScoreReference'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
  /animal/{identifier}/weights:
    get:
      description: Returns the weights for the specified animal
      operationId: findWeights
      parameters:
        - name: identifier
          in: path
          description: primary identifier for the animal
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: weights response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscWeightEventResource'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
    post:
      description: Uploads new weight for the animal
      operationId: addWeight
      parameters:
        - name: identifier
          in: path
          description: primary identifier for the animal
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        description: new weight event for the animal
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscWeightEventResource'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: weight response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscWeightEventResource'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
    put:
      description: Updates the weight events for the specified animal
      operationId: updateWeights
      parameters:
        - name: identifier
          in: path
          description: primary identifier for the animal
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        description: Updated weight events for the animal
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscWeightEventResource'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: animal response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: 'https://github.com/AndyDe-Aldent/animal_schema/blob/feature/LifeDataSwaggerSpec/JSON_Schemas/Weights_and_Condition_Scores/iscWeightEventResource'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
components:
  schemas:
    Error:
      type: object
      required:
        - code
        - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
